  "title": "SERVICE CREW",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Provide quality customer service and housekeeping duties</li><li>Assist in opening and closing of the outlet</li><li>Prepare and serve foods to customer</li><li>Marketing menu items to customers</li><li>Handle cashiering duties</li><li>Able to handle customers skillfully to ensure full satisfaction</li><li>Establish rapport with guests</li><li>Maintain clear records of stocks and inventories</li><li>Any other duties as assigned</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>No experience in similar field is required</li><li>F&B Hygiene Certificate</li><li>Excellent communication skills</li><li>Commitment to quality service</li><li>Service excellence</li><li>Food and Beverage knowledge</li></ul>",
