    "description": "<p>Mandate of Manpower Pte. Ltd. (UEN 201837939H) (F.K.A. Mandate of Old Times Pte. Ltd.) was founded&nbsp;in 2018. We provide a manpower solutions which allows clients to source cleaning and general staffing from us.</p>\n<p>At Mandate of Manpower, we specialise in providing high quality part-time residential cleaning services. We aim to have effective communication with our clients which allows our services to be effective. We also supply multiple different labour solutions for both hotels and events. Hotel services include housekeeping and public area attendants while stewards can be supplied to events.</p>",
